@startuml
title UC13 - Frontend Classes
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
class TeamAdminPage { +loadTeams(): void +openEditor(): void +sync(): void }
class TeamEditorForm { team +validate(): ValidationResult +save(): void }
class TeamLogo { logoUrl +render(): JSX }
class PlayerList { players +render(): JSX }
class PlayerAvatar { imageUrl +render(): JSX }
class TeamApiClient {
  +list(): Promise<Team[]>
  +create(dto): Promise<Team>
  +update(id,dto): Promise<Team>
  +remove(id): Promise<void>
  +sync(): Promise<SyncResult>
}
TeamAdminPage --> TeamEditorForm
TeamAdminPage --> PlayerList
TeamEditorForm --> TeamLogo
PlayerList --> PlayerAvatar
TeamAdminPage --> TeamApiClient
note bottom of TeamLogo
  Thiếu logoUrl/imageUrl -> hiển thị ảnh mặc định.
end note
@enduml
